Class GameMaze3dModel

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • model.GameMaze3dModel
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Model

    public class GameMaze3dModel
extends java.util.Observable
implements Model

    GameMaze3dModel

    Implements all Model interface functoins. Also save all mazes created / loaded and their's solution if were solved.

    Author:
    Valentina Munoz & Moris Amon

      • solveMaze

        public void solveMaze(algorithms.search.Searcher<algorithms.mazeGenerators.Position> searcher,
                      java.lang.String name,
                      java.lang.String type,
                      algorithms.search.State<algorithms.mazeGenerators.Position> state)
        Description copied from interface: Model

        solveMaze

        Solve maze wanted according to the type ("hint" or "solve") and algorithm received. If state is not null, it change the initial position of the maze to it, so it calculte the solution from that position. When finish, it throws a notification to the presenter to display it.

        Specified by:
        solveMaze in interface Model
        Parameters:
        searcher - The searcher algorithm class
        name - The maze name
        type - solution wanted. "hint" for half solution and back or "solve" for entaire solution
        state - a state from which the solution should be calculated
